-- Per-civ section header icon override.
-- DLC variant civs do not have civ_flags/ images; we use the most
-- dedicated game civ flag for each DLC variant. Base civs (those that
-- have flag_<civ>.png via _PlayerUI_RaceImage) are omitted — they resolve
-- through Tier-1 / Tier-2. Flag stems confirmed from ui/images/civ_flags/
-- in cardinal-ui SGA data.
