-- Keys are the "base token" extracted from the SBP name by
-- _sbp_base_token(): strip "unit_" prefix, stop before "_<tier>_".
-- Keys with tier suffix (e.g. trebuchet_4) are tried first.
--
-- CONFIRMED: canonical icon_name from game_data/generated/canonical/
--   ebp-unit-stats.json or direct WPFGUI codebase reference.
-- HEURISTIC: follow races/{civ}/units/<token>.png convention;
--   absent paths render as nothing in WPF — group icon is the
--   fallback inside the card header, card body just stays blank.
